oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Panel Discussion
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Panel discussion on use of curette in treating retroarticular abscess, the method of preparing teaser bulls using the so-called unwedding ring, criteria to evaluate preventing a lateral luxation of the patella in large calves, the calf with the lateral subluxation, treatment of abscesses of the sole, deformities as calving problems.
